00:17:36,530 --> 00:17:38,880
However, it's ineffective against at least
some

250
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:42,720
protozoa and requires longer contact times
for viruses.

251
00:17:44,110 --> 00:17:46,160
Chlorine does give a residual protection

252
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:50,113
which can help minimize recontamination or
regrowth.

253
00:17:50,113 --> 00:17:54,410
But it has a characteristic taste and odor
which people

