263
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:25,780
So, in summary, chlorine is a widely used

264
00:18:25,780 --> 00:18:29,590
disinfectant in both conventional
treatment and household water treatment.

265
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:34,060
Chlorine can be obtained from a wide
variety of sources, but all

266
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:38,309
of these produce free chlorine in water,
which is the active disinfectant.

